properties.description:
Repurpose the existing, under-utilized bayfront parking lot (Parking lot #5) by creating green space for activities like yoga, pilates, stretching and relaxing while including benches for our community to congregate in front of the beautiful bay;    
Take down the fence running along the west side of the boathouse (which the city of Miami will do at no cost) and repurpose the area between pool, concession stand, and the boat launch/parking lot.  
Create waterfront walking/bike trail, including vita course equipment at proper locations, connecting the south side of the existing pedestrian trail, around the volleyball court and connecting again to the existing trail north of the pool.

